<p><b>Garry Meier</b> (born December 2, 1949) is a <a href="Chicago" title="Chicago">Chicago</a>-based <a href="Radio_personality" title="Radio personality">radio personality</a> and is currently the afternoon host on WGN-AM 720 in Chicago, heard weekdays 3-7 PM CT.</p>
